    "title": "Looking for Real Estate Agent at 99acres",
    "description": "99acres has an exciting opening for a Real Estate Agent at our Madurai office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout 99acres:\n99acres is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Client Relationship Management\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 99acres!",
